# Test Kuralları

## Dosya Konumu

Co-located: `__tests__/` veya `*.spec.ts` — test edilen modülle aynı dizin.

## Naming

```typescript
describe('PolicyGuard', () => {
  it('should deny action_owner accessing unassigned case', () => { ... });
  it('should allow council_secretary with sufficient clearance', () => { ... });
});
```

Karar traceability: test adında ilgili karar ID mümkünse (`AUTH-006`).

## Mock Stratejisi

Mock at boundary — KMS, S3, SMTP, ClamAV, OIDC. Internal module mock yasak.

## Factory Pattern

`packages/test-fixtures` — faker + typed factory. Manuel object yaratma yasak. Sentetik veri only.

## Integration Test

Testcontainers PostgreSQL — production DB'ye bağlanma yasak. Transaction rollback per-test tercih.

## Workflow Transition Matrix

Her geçiş minimum 8 senaryo: pozitif, yanlış rol, yanlış state, clearance, atama dışı, idempotency, side-effect, precondition fail.

Detay: `Docs/08_TESTING_STRATEGY.md` §4 tablo.

## Security Test

SAST/SCA/secret/container scan CI gate — skip yasak.

## Anti-pattern'ler

- Happy path only authorization test
- Production seed test ortamında
- Implementation detail assertion (call count) over behavior

